T*
(  `InputSystemUIInputModule`.) Tj
T*
(4. `CaseScreenController.OnEnable\(\)` auto-binds UI, ensures runtime overlays exist, and) Tj
T*
(  either opens case selection or applies the current case directly.) Tj
