(Runtime Data Model) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(- Runtime case data is ScriptableObject-driven.) Tj
T*
(- Primary data assets:) Tj
T*
(  - `Assets/Scripts/Cases/CaseDefinitionSO.cs`) Tj
T*
(  - `Assets/Scripts/Cases/SuspectProfileSO.cs`) Tj
T*
(  - `Assets/Scripts/Cases/EvidenceProfileSO.cs`) Tj
T*
(  - `Assets/Scripts/Cases/CaseLibrarySO.cs`) Tj
T*
(- Core shape assumptions are fixed across the runtime and tooling:) Tj
T*
(  - exactly 5 suspects) Tj
T*
(  - exactly 3 evidence items) Tj
T*
(  - 1 guilty suspect slot) Tj
T*
T*
(Frontend / UI Features In The Scene) Tj
