(Case Content Pipeline) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(The case workflow is a separate local authoring and rendering pipeline.) Tj
T*
T*
(Canonical flow:) Tj
T*
T*
(1. Author case JSON in `case_workflow/cases/`) Tj
T*
(2. Validate content with `case_workflow/validate_case_schema.py`) Tj
T*
(3. Build prompt queues via `case_workflow/src/case_workflow/prompt_builder.py`) Tj
T*
(4. Render images with `case_workflow/render_case.py`) Tj
T*
(5. Emit a Unity import bundle under `Assets/GeneratedCases/to_import/<CASE_ID>`) Tj
T*
(6. Sync or import into curated Unity assets using:) Tj
T*
(   - `case_workflow/sync_curated_cases.py`) Tj
T*
(   - or `Assets/Editor/GeneratedCaseImporter.cs`) Tj
T*
(7. Verify the case in the Unity scene) Tj
T*
T*
(Source Of Truth And Curated Content) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(- The authoring source of truth is JSON in `case_workflow/cases/`.) Tj
T*
(- The generated import bundle in `Assets/GeneratedCases/to_import/` is staging output, not) Tj
T*
(  authoritative source content.) Tj
T*
(- Curated in-project Unity case assets currently live under `Assets/Scripts/Cases/CASE_*`.) Tj
T*
(- Current curated set appears to be `CASE_009` through `CASE_014`.) Tj
T*
T*
(Tooling And Stack) Tj
T*
T*
T*
(### Unity Side) Tj
T*
T*
(- Unity 6 / `6000.4.0f1`) Tj
T*
(- uGUI, not UIToolkit) Tj
T*
(- Universal Render Pipeline) Tj
T*
(- Input System package installed) Tj
T*
(- Unity Test Framework package installed, though practical test coverage is thin) Tj
T*
T*
(### Python Pipeline Side) Tj
T*
T*
(- Python `>=3.10`) Tj
T*
(- Reusable Python modules live in `case_workflow/src/case_workflow/`) Tj
T*
(- Primary modules:) Tj
T*
ET
