(### Experimental / Supporting Tools) Tj
T*
T*
(- `case_workflow/gradio_flux2_studio.py` provides a local manual image-generation UI) Tj
T*
(- Qwen and FLUX-related scripts/docs exist, but they are clearly auxiliary to the main) Tj
T*
